- Stop!

500
00:40:24,470 --> 00:40:25,470
What happened?

501
00:40:25,470 --> 00:40:26,560
There are assassins in the palace!

502
00:40:26,560 --> 00:40:28,020
You must be careful!

503
00:40:28,020 --> 00:40:30,340
Someone's trying to assassinate Tantai Jin?

504
00:41:14,730 --> 00:41:16,220
Let them go.

505
00:41:16,220 --> 00:41:18,300
Are you going to kill me?

506
00:41:19,650 --> 00:41:23,460
Xiao Lin, the conflict between the two kingdoms just ended not long ago.

507
00:41:23,460 --> 00:41:25,480
The world is gradually regaining peace.

508
00:41:25,480 --> 00:41:27,340
If you kill me today,

509
00:41:27,340 --> 00:41:31,240
the two kingdoms will descend into chaos again.

510
00:41:31,240 --> 00:41:33,280
Countless people will die.

511
00:41:33,280 --> 00:41:35,030
You know that...

512
00:41:35,860 --> 00:41:38,240
better than anyone.

513
00:41:38,860 --> 00:41:43,240
That's why you won't kill me.

514
00:42:02,300 --> 00:42:06,590
Why are you here today?

515
00:42:15,610 --> 00:42:19,720
I want you to pull back your troops and end the war.

516
00:42:23,050 --> 00:42:25,170
A fair request.

517
00:42:26,690 --> 00:42:28,680
But it's a shame.

518
00:42:30,750 --> 00:42:32,670
Today,

519
00:42:35,960 --> 00:42:39,270
you don't get to bargain with me.

520
00:42:53,820 --> 00:42:56,430
You knew I was going to assassinate you tonight?

521
00:43:00,860 --> 00:43:03,160
Every inch of land is my territory now.

522
00:43:03,160 --> 00:43:07,740
Now, my eyes and ears are everywhere.

523
00:43:07,740 --> 00:43:10,570
My informant will tell me everything, including when you made your plan

524
00:43:10,570 --> 00:43:12,780
and when you will set off.

525
00:43:14,080 --> 00:43:16,740
Today, Prince Xuancheng, you came here uninvited.

526
00:43:16,740 --> 00:43:21,540
It would be rude of me not to give you a warm welcome.

527
00:43:43,430 --> 00:43:45,360
I admit defeat.

528
00:43:48,880 --> 00:43:50,430
Kneel.

529
00:43:55,190 --> 00:44:01,280
Xiao Lin, is this all that's left of the Secret Dragon Guards?

530
00:44:01,280 --> 00:44:04,040
Where are your two trusted followers?

531
00:44:14,650 --> 00:44:19,140
Madam Xuancheng, where are you going in the middle of the night?

532
00:44:19,140 --> 00:44:22,030
<i>Seems like Xiao Lin failed.</i>

533
00:44:22,030 --> 00:44:24,410
How dare you kidnap me?

534
00:44:24,410 --> 00:44:27,000
Chief Pian, they wanted to kidnap me.

535
00:44:27,000 --> 00:44:28,790
Save me!

536
00:44:30,690 --> 00:44:33,300
You guys heard that, right?

537
00:44:33,300 --> 00:44:35,340
What a bunch of foolish men.

538
00:44:35,340 --> 00:44:37,750
You all can't even figure this out?

539
00:44:43,150 --> 00:44:45,040
Tantai Jin!

540
00:44:47,090 --> 00:44:49,040
Tantai Jin!

541
00:44:50,090 --> 00:44:52,500
Why are you here at such a late hour?

542
00:44:52,500 --> 00:44:54,410
Are you okay? Were you hurt?

543
00:44:54,410 --> 00:44:56,990
Don't worry. I'm fine.

544
00:44:56,990 --> 00:44:58,650
I was terrified.

545
00:44:58,650 --> 00:45:01,760
Look at you. Your hands are freezing.

546
00:45:10,950 --> 00:45:13,050
Do you feel better now?

547
00:45:18,020 --> 00:45:20,490
Xiao Lin?

548
00:45:20,490 --> 00:45:22,830
<i>Xiao Lin was the one who tried to assassinate Tantai Jin?</i>

549
00:45:22,830 --> 00:45:24,060
<i>What should I do?</i>

550
00:45:24,060 --> 00:45:26,250
It's been a long time, Second Young Miss.

551
00:45:29,980 --> 00:45:32,650
- Well…
- You'd better not ask me

552
00:45:32,650 --> 00:45:35,920
to show him mercy at this moment.

553
00:45:38,000 --> 00:45:40,410
Thank you for your kindness, Second Young Miss.

554
00:45:40,410 --> 00:45:43,130
I was aware of the consequences.

555
00:45:44,000 --> 00:45:45,830
<i>Report!</i>

556
00:45:46,730 --> 00:45:47,470
Report!

557
00:45:47,470 --> 00:45:50,730
Chief Pianran has intercepted the rebels who kidnapped Madam Xuancheng.

558
00:45:50,730 --> 00:45:53,750
Your Majesty, don't worry. Madam Xuancheng is fine.

559
00:45:53,750 --> 00:45:56,220
Good. Tell Pianran to bring her here.

560
00:45:56,220 --> 00:45:57,670
I need to ask her something.

561
00:45:57,670 --> 00:45:59,210
Yes, Your Majesty.

562
00:46:05,980 --> 00:46:07,570
Run!

563
00:46:10,400 --> 00:46:11,530
What?

564
00:46:11,530 --> 00:46:15,090
Don't tell me you want me to help you up?

565
00:46:16,380 --> 00:46:19,030
I wasn't on their side.

566
00:46:19,030 --> 00:46:23,930
Please clarify the truth in front of His Majesty on my behalf.

567
00:46:25,130 --> 00:46:26,900
Is that so?

568
00:46:38,090 --> 00:46:40,150
Why do you possess it?

569
00:46:40,820 --> 00:46:42,230
What do you mean?

570
00:46:42,230 --> 00:46:43,300
Speak!

571
00:46:43,300 --> 00:46:48,050
Why do you possess that love thread?

572
00:46:51,350 --> 00:46:54,260
I don't know!

573
00:46:54,260 --> 00:46:55,810
Let go of me!

574
00:46:55,810 --> 00:46:58,030
I'm a distinguished guest of His Majesty.

575
00:46:58,030 --> 00:46:59,800
I'm going to ask you one last time.

576
00:46:59,800 --> 00:47:04,300
Where did you get that love thread?

577
00:47:05,130 --> 00:47:08,080
Do you really think I'm as stupid as them?

578
00:47:08,080 --> 00:47:12,360
You think I can't do anything to you if you don't talk?

579
00:47:22,130 --> 00:47:22,980
Let go.

580
00:47:22,980 --> 00:47:24,580
Pianran, calm down.

581
00:47:24,580 --> 00:47:26,180
There's no need for violence.

582
00:47:26,830 --> 00:47:29,950
Qingyu, she's trying to kill me.

583
00:47:29,950 --> 00:47:31,430
Qingyu.

584
00:47:31,430 --> 00:47:33,080
No matter what my sister has done,

585
00:47:33,080 --> 00:47:34,600
I'll apologize to you on her behalf.

586
00:47:34,600 --> 00:47:37,990
Let's straighten things out first.

587
00:47:38,610 --> 00:47:40,320
I've got nothing to straighten out with you.

588
00:47:40,320 --> 00:47:41,880
Out of my way!

589
00:47:55,240 --> 00:47:56,950
Get lost.

590
00:47:56,950 --> 00:47:58,480
Get lost!

591
00:47:59,050 --> 00:48:03,950
Pianran, I heard you mention something about a love thread just now.

592
00:48:03,950 --> 00:48:06,020
What exactly is going on?

593
00:48:07,630 --> 00:48:08,780
It's none of your business.

594
00:48:08,780 --> 00:48:10,980
How could that be?

595
00:48:10,980 --> 00:48:14,350
Chief, His Majesty has ordered you to bring Madam Xuancheng to the main hall.

596
00:48:28,530 --> 00:48:31,540
Sir, I failed to complete my mission.

597
00:48:31,540 --> 00:48:32,380
How come?

598
00:48:32,380 --> 00:48:34,220
Eldest Young Miss Ye claimed that we kidnapped her.

599
00:48:34,220 --> 00:48:36,300
She was unwilling to leave with us.

600
00:48:38,420 --> 00:48:41,220
Why would Xiao Lin fall for someone like her?

601
00:48:41,220 --> 00:48:44,460
Scholar Pang, what should we do now?

602
00:48:45,530 --> 00:48:48,960
Leave the capital in small groups as per His Highness's instruction.

603
00:48:48,960 --> 00:48:50,970
After that, join up with Chen Xian's main force.

604
00:48:50,970 --> 00:48:52,370
Yes, sir.

605
00:48:52,370 --> 00:48:53,940
Let's go.

606
00:48:55,000 --> 00:48:59,900
Prince Xuancheng, it might be too sentimental for you to meet your wife in a foreign land.

607
00:48:59,900 --> 00:49:04,570
Why don't you wait behind the hall for a while?

608
00:49:06,830 --> 00:49:08,380
Please.

609
00:49:13,210 --> 00:49:14,860
What's the matter?

610
00:49:16,380 --> 00:49:18,350
I'll keep an eye on him for you.

611
00:49:22,860 --> 00:49:24,990
Were you hurt?

612
00:49:24,990 --> 00:49:28,690
Out of all the things to do, why did you put your neck into the noose?

613
00:49:28,690 --> 00:49:30,610
Report!

614
00:49:31,340 --> 00:49:35,500
Report! Chief Pianran, General Ye, and Madam Xuancheng are here to seek an audience.

615
00:49:35,500 --> 00:49:37,190
Let them in.

616
00:49:37,190 --> 00:49:38,660
Yes, Your Majesty.

617
00:49:49,380 --> 00:49:52,350
<i>In the end, Bingchang still couldn't make it out.</i>

618
00:49:52,350 --> 00:49:56,810
Madam Xuancheng contributed the most to the assassins' capture tonight.

619
00:49:56,810 --> 00:49:58,940
She deserves the highest award.

620
00:49:58,940 --> 00:50:00,540
Thank you, Your Majesty.

621
00:50:00,540 --> 00:50:04,340
I'm honored to resolve your troubles for you.

622
00:50:04,340 --> 00:50:06,250
I…

623
00:50:06,250 --> 00:50:08,280
dare not take credit for it.

624
00:50:08,780 --> 00:50:10,320
What does that mean?

625
00:50:10,320 --> 00:50:12,260
What has Eldest Sister got to do with this operation?

626
00:50:12,260 --> 00:50:14,960
You had the idea to send Xiao Lin a letter with encrypted messages

627
00:50:14,960 --> 00:50:17,870
to make him believe that your life was in danger.

628
00:50:17,870 --> 00:50:21,120
You asked for his help urgently with the letter you wrote.

629
00:50:21,120 --> 00:50:27,820
A chivalrous man like Xiao Lin would definitely come to your rescue personally.

630
00:50:27,820 --> 00:50:29,980
This is a devious scheme that takes advantage of human nature.

631
00:50:29,980 --> 00:50:34,250
You have outdone most of my advisers.

632
00:50:34,250 --> 00:50:36,140
I'm flattered, Your Majesty.

633
00:50:39,460 --> 00:50:42,600
But I'm curious about something.

634
00:50:42,600 --> 00:50:47,880
What if Xiao Lin succeeded in assassinating me tonight?

635
00:50:47,880 --> 00:50:52,870
Would you swim with the current and leave together with him?

636
00:50:55,200 --> 00:50:56,800
Your Majesty, please give us your wise judgment.

637
00:50:56,800 --> 00:51:01,830
I had cut off all ties with Xiao Lin ever since I came back from the Sheng Kingdom.

638
00:51:01,830 --> 00:51:03,880
Eldest Sister, you…

639
00:51:12,460 --> 00:51:18,320
<i>[Till The End of the Moon]</i>

640
00:51:27,010 --> 00:51:31,880
<i>[Black Moonlight - Zhang Bichen and Mao Buyi]</i>

641
00:51:31,880 --> 00:51:39,680
♫ <i>Mortal desires are like gazing upon the sudden disappearance of the moon</i> ♫

642
00:51:39,680 --> 00:51:47,380
♫ <i>The mortal world is like three thousand flowers in the midst of a snowstorm</i> ♫

643
00:51:47,380 --> 00:51:55,300
♫ <i>Compassion is embracing a butterfly during times of ruin and pain</i> ♫

644
00:51:55,300 --> 00:51:59,180
♫ <i>Realization is washing away our memories in turbid water and rain</i> ♫

645
00:51:59,180 --> 00:52:03,790
♫ <i>We'll never meet again</i> ♫

646
00:52:04,880 --> 00:52:08,540
♫ <i>I've seen the flowers bloom from soft-spoken words</i> ♫

647
00:52:08,540 --> 00:52:12,180
♫ <i>Teary-eyed till all that's left was nonsense</i> ♫

648
00:52:12,180 --> 00:52:16,660
♫ <i>Love intertwines around the fragile titled roof</i> ♫

649
00:52:16,660 --> 00:52:20,380
♫ <i>Embracing the endless lingering fear</i> ♫

650
00:52:20,380 --> 00:52:24,020
♫ <i>I've admired you through the myriad of years</i> ♫

651
00:52:24,020 --> 00:52:28,200
♫ <i>I believed I have been loved for a moment</i> ♫

652
00:52:28,200 --> 00:52:31,800
♫ <i>I plucked the dark feathers that shrouded my body in evil</i> ♫

653
00:52:31,800 --> 00:52:39,860
♫ <i>And become devout like the flawless moonlight</i> ♫

654
00:52:41,660 --> 00:52:45,360
♫ <i>Listen to the breathing of the flowers</i> ♫

655
00:52:45,360 --> 00:52:49,080
♫ <i>and how they are just like any other creature</i> ♫

656
00:52:49,080 --> 00:52:53,440
♫ <i>No matter how far we walk, through the dust, wind, and stars</i> ♫

657
00:52:53,440 --> 00:52:57,240
♫ <i>The moonlight is my armor</i> ♫

658
00:52:57,240 --> 00:53:00,760
♫ <i>I'd admire your arrival when you came covered in scars</i> ♫

659
00:53:00,760 --> 00:53:04,720
♫ <i>And willingness to live a life in peace</i> ♫

660
00:53:04,720 --> 00:53:08,600
<i>You plucked the dark feathers that shrouded your body in evil</i> ♫

661
00:53:08,600 --> 00:53:16,540
♫ <i>And learned to love what you used to resent</i> ♫

662
00:53:16,540 --> 00:53:24,340
♫ <i>Despite living insignificant lives, our dreams are as big as the sky</i> ♫

663
00:53:24,340 --> 00:53:33,980
♫ <i>And we'll make it something to remember us by</i> ♫
